                            <b>8. PROGRAM DESIGN </b></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding-top:5px; text-align:justify;">
                        The DFMA Program consists of 4 Modules and each Module comprises of two papers each; in all, four Modules totaling eight papers. Each Module will be taught online and after completion of each paper, the candidate has to submit an assignment. There will be exercises at the end of each unit to assess self-learning; these self-learning exercises will not be graded. An online examination will be held after the completion of each module. It is mandatory for all the students to undertake and complete a project work as well.   
